Why I can't get
electrical properties

00:12:28.750 --> 00:12:32.670
with classical potentials?

00:12:32.670 --> 00:12:33.360
Yeah.

00:12:33.360 --> 00:12:35.880
AUDIENCE: Because you're
modeling the entire atoms.

