00:13:00.480 --> 00:13:02.020
like this, and this.

00:13:04.590 --> 00:13:06.480
It's really powerful.

00:13:06.480 --> 00:13:08.250
And it tells you--
and so all we need

00:13:08.250 --> 00:13:10.680
to do is go down one
more scale, because this

00:13:10.680 --> 00:13:14.310
