00:43:01.880 --> 00:43:05.750
is that, until you measure it--

00:43:05.750 --> 00:43:07.670
you see, the little
radioactive thing

00:43:07.670 --> 00:43:10.230
is a very quantum
mechanical particle.

00:43:10.230 --> 00:43:17.160
So until you measure it, as with
the electron, it's everywhere.

00:43:17.160 --> 00:43:21.600
It's both emitted and
released the poison and not.

00:43:21.600 --> 00:43:23.500
The state is quantum mechanical.

00:43:23.500 --> 00:43:27.390
And so what Schrodinger did is
he said, well, that's absurd.

00:43:27.390 --> 00:43:31.590
Because then if you take that
up to the macroscopic levels,

00:43:31.590 --> 00:43:33.300
you can get these
sort of absurdities.

00:43:33.300 --> 00:43:34.860
And that's why he
came up with this,

00:43:34.860 --> 00:43:38.400
actually to make a point that
we don't understand this yet.

00:43:38.400 --> 00:43:39.990
That was really the point here.

00:43:39.990 --> 00:43:42.100
And this paradox has been--

00:43:42.100 --> 00:43:43.950
and so, because the
point being the cat

00:43:43.950 --> 00:43:46.350
is both dead and alive
according to quantum mechanics.

00:43:46.350 --> 00:43:47.260
It is both.

00:43:47.260 --> 00:43:50.910
It is a superposition
of dead and alive

00:43:50.910 --> 00:43:53.657
until you open the box, in which
case, you collapse the wave

00:43:53.657 --> 00:43:54.990
function because you observe it.

00:43:58.290 --> 00:44:01.620
That would be really what
quantum mechanics tells you.

00:44:01.620 --> 00:44:08.370
And this paradox has been
one of the central talking

00:44:08.370 --> 00:44:10.200
points of quantum
mechanics, or examples

00:44:10.200 --> 00:44:15.780
used to illustrate how
strange quantum mechanics is

00:44:15.780 --> 00:44:16.543
for many decades.

00:44:16.543 --> 00:44:18.210
And it's also led to
a lot of discussion

00:44:18.210 --> 00:44:21.780
on how we should actually
interpret quantum mechanics.

00:44:21.780 --> 00:44:24.473
This is called the
Copenhagen interpretation,

00:44:24.473 --> 00:44:26.640
for those of you who are
interested in reading more,

00:44:26.640 --> 00:44:27.840
but there are many, many others.

