00:44:34.050 --> 00:44:35.280
of quantum mechanics.

00:44:35.280 --> 00:44:36.480
How cool is that?

00:44:36.480 --> 00:44:40.830
We really don't know
what this all means.

00:44:40.830 --> 00:44:42.270
And that's pretty neat.

